Reinforcement Learning, Theory. 

Reinforcement learning is the main focus of the paper, as the authors propose a multiagent Q-learning method for finding optimal strategies in general-sum stochastic games. 

Theory is also a relevant sub-category, as the paper presents a theoretical framework for multiagent reinforcement learning in general-sum stochastic games, and proves the convergence of the proposed algorithm under certain conditions.
